quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  8,26,"Ciftoree tuma ngonndo…óon fam…óu…ďe, lo'inaa…ďe ka leydi, ho…óon kula nde yim…ďe …ďen jilotoo on. O weerni (tappion), O semmbiniri on ballal makko ngal, O arsiki on immorde e laa…ďu…ói mbelejo'o, on njettatmo e( dokke makko …óe)."
  8,27,"Eehey mon gooŇč…óin…ďe, wata on jamfo Alla e Nulaa…óo on, jamfo…óon koolaaje mon …óen hara hi…óon nganndi."
  8,28,"Nganndee pellet, jaw…óe mon …óen e …ďi…ó…ďe mon …ďen ko fitina e won de no ka Alla njo…ďdi mawndi."
  8,29,"Eehey mon gooŇč…óin…ďe, si on kulii Alla, O wa…óanay on ceerndir…óum (goonga e meere), O heefana on bakkatuuji mon O haforana on. Alla ko Jom-…ďural mawnungal."
  8,30,"(siftor) tuma nde heefer…ďe …ďeen fewjanayno maa fii yo…ďe nannguma maa, …ďe mbar maa, …ďe njaltinmaa. He…ďe pewja, Alla no fewja. Ko Alla …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude fewjoo…ďe …ďeen."
  8,31,"Si Aayeeje amen …óeen janngaama e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbi'a : "GooŇč…óii men nanii, sinno men ynji…óno…óuno min kaalatno yeru …óum, ndee wonaani si wonaa tinndi adinoo…ďe"."
  8,32,"E tuma …ďe mbiunoo : "Yaa Alla, si tawii ko …óum woni goonga immorde ka Maa…óa, haray saa∆īin kaa∆īe e amen immorde ka kammu, maa addanaa men lepte mu'usu…óe"."
  8,33,"Alla wonaani leptoowo …ďe, hara an ha…óa hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Alla siforaalni leptoowo …ďe, hara kam…ďe he…ďe imsinaade."